title: GDG DevFest 2015 Announced
brief: Silicon Valley GDGs are proud to announce GDG DevFest 2015. Like last year, the event will be held on November 21 in Mountain View, CA. Set aside all your business at this time and make plans to head to the Googleplex.

title: Call for Speakers
brief: We're very excited - not just because of the inordinate amount of caffeine based products consumed - but also because our team is putting together the final missing parts to the biggest Google related event in Silicon Valley - GDG DevFest 2015. Sign-up here to become a speaker!
